headline: SGH and Charles River team up for CGMP cell banking services
summary: SGH will process cord blood to develop and produce allogeneic chimeric antigen receptor (CAR) T-cells designed for cancer treatment.

headline: Charles River Announces Agreement with Singapore General Hospital
summary: WILMINGTON, Mass., February 25, 2025--Charles River to provide master cell banking and NGS testing services for SGH's cord blood derived allogeneic CAR-T cells.
